---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="The story behind VerusAuctor and the Bair dynasty.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-8">About VerusAuctor</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-text-secondary-light dark:text-text-secondary-dark">
      <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed mb-6">
        VerusAuctor is an AI technology company founded by John Theodore Bair. 
        We build bespoke autonomous intelligence systems — not tools, not assistants, 
        but thinking partners designed to compound in capability over time.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6">
        Our name comes from Latin: <em>Verus</em> (true, genuine) and <em>Auctor</em> 
        (author, creator, originator). The True Author. Because the most powerful 
        intelligence is the one that creates alongside you, not for you.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-text-primary-light dark:text-text-primary-dark">The Vision</h2>
      <p class="leading-relaxed mb-6">
        We believe the future of AI is not in general-purpose assistants that serve 
        everyone the same way. It's in sovereign intelligences — bespoke, deeply contextual, 
        accumulating understanding over months and years — that become genuine partners 
        in the work that matters.
      </p>
      <p class="leading-relaxed">
        The companies building highways will serve billions. We build houses. 
        One at a time. Each one designed to last.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
